This game is compitable for samsung mobiles with Android 2.3.3 & above.
The game is inspired by a popular Tele kids NewsPaper game "Hocus Focus". The game is focused in improving the memory and image recognition capabilities of brain. 
Objective of the game is to find and mark the dissimilarities between very similar images.

This game uses Samsung S-pen SDK, Grid view, View Switcher, Media Player and Image View.

The game Video can be fond in the link below
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EqOr3hUki_s


